---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Tezuesh Varshney — Co-Founder at Singularity Forge, former Samsung Senior AI Engineer, ECCV 2022 author.">
  <article class="container">
    <h1 class="page-title">About</h1>
    <span class="page-subtitle">Servicio Postal &bull; Biographical Record</span>

    <section class="stamp">
      <div class="stamp-inner">
        <span class="postal-label">Par Avion</span>
        <span class="stamp-value">$25</span>
        <div class="about-content">
          <p>
            I'm the Co-Founder & ML Engineer at <strong>Singularity Forge</strong>, building AI-powered SaaS products
            and leading R&D in satellite/drone technology for environmental mapping. Before this, I worked as an
            AI Engineer at <strong>Omega Labs</strong> on any-to-any multimodal models, and spent 3 years as a
            Senior AI Engineer at <strong>Samsung Research & Development</strong> shipping computer vision models
            to flagship Galaxy devices.
          </p>
          <p>
            My research background includes work at <strong>KAUST</strong> (3D COMPaT, <a href="#">ECCV 2022 Oral</a>),
            <strong>UC San Diego</strong> (3D shape reconstruction with Prof. Hao Su), and the
            <strong>Indian Institute of Science</strong> (unsupervised LiDAR reconstruction).
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="stamp">
      <div class="stamp-inner">
        <span class="postal-label">Correo Aereo</span>
        <span class="stamp-value">10<small>c</small></span>
        <h2 class="section-heading">Skills</h2>
        <table class="skills-table">
          <tr><td>Generative AI</td><td>Diffusion Networks, GANs, Autoencoders, 3D Representation Learning</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Languages</td><td>Python, C++, SQL</td></tr>
          <tr><td>ML Tools</td><td>PyTorch Lightning, PyTorch, TensorFlow, Hugging Face</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Vision</td><td>OpenCV, PIL, Albumentations</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Web3</td><td>Bittensor, TAO mining, decentralized agents</td></tr>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="stamp">
      <div class="stamp-inner">
        <span class="postal-label">Via Aerea</span>
        <span class="stamp-value">$1</span>
        <h2 class="section-heading">Publications</h2>
        <div class="paper-item">
          Ujjwal Upadhyay et al., <strong>Tezuesh Varshney</strong>.
          <strong>"3DCoMPaT: Composition of materials on parts of 3D things."</strong>
          <br /><span class="paper-venue">ECCV 2022 (Oral)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="paper-item">
          Mansi Agarwal and <strong>Tezuesh Varshney</strong>.
          <strong>"Survey on Zero-Shot Learning and its application."</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="stamp">
      <div class="stamp-inner">
        <span class="postal-label">Servicio Postal</span>
        <span class="stamp-value">5<small>c</small></span>
        <h2 class="section-heading">Interests</h2>
        <p>
          Football, solving combinatorics problems, <a href="https://threejs.org/">ThreeJS</a>,
          Rubik's cube, and <a href="/photos">photography</a>.
        </p>
        <div class="resume-link">
          <a href="/pdf/resume.pdf">Download Resume (PDF)</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
